{"tid":1682832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［全民健身］呢派好中意做運動行上行落","createTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T11:15:27.000Z","uid":144084,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cf2ea6200231217b00ace552fe2447d689adc014","tid":1682832,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:49.000Z","msg":"得閒落街執兩舊磚上天台<br />\n好健康哦～<br />\n<br />\n不如趁未有Event 大家一齊做運動<br />\n<br />\n唔一定自己天台的親～"},{"pid":"51fed90657a9ed219728974d5915d0a3dd7fe35b","tid":1682832,"uid":1477,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:22.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<br />\n佢地班口撐支那唔緊要<br />\n肉體懼怕支那先最實際<br />\n正如有d 人口裡反美心，身體卻去食元氣<br />\n呢d 真係唔太實際囉<br />\n<br />\n為左節流<br />\n大家快d share 文宣比長者睇<br />\n支那嘅恐怖真係隨時影響到香港<br />\n到時棺材都無埋就好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3ADQhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3ADQhD.jpg&h=fbfa3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L003CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L003CF.jpg&h=0bf8c277&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"026e39934bd28081d19170d07ad12d1d94ebfc7d","tid":1682832,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:42.000Z","msg":"和理非都可以一齊練下體能噢～ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e5230866531753682cf7c3239edeea49bf58be","tid":1682832,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:51:57.000Z","msg":"更細更分散嘅攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1677737\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1677737</a><br />\n睇落去啲留言有講點做<br />\n旺旺, 青島, 獅球嘜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a09cb1b4b4005982440130059caf11183010a37c","tid":1682832,"uid":287547,"like":0,"